These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: crime, mystery, western, epic, thriller, spy, musical
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: pop, funk, techno, house, disco, dubstep, gospel
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, skateboarding, skiing, snowboarding, basketball, lacrosse
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the fan of funk and the fan of pop##2
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the fan of funk is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the fan of house is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person watching thriller movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person watching musical movies is the fan of techno##1
11. the fan of dubstep is the person watching epic movies##1
12. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
13. the person who's sport is cricket is the fan of disco##1
14. the person watching spy movies is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | spy | mystery | epic | musical  | western  |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | house        | funk  | gospel     | dubstep   | techno       | disco   |
| Sport         | cycling   | lacrosse | skiing    | skateboarding  | snowboarding | basketball | cricket |

