.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, chinese, malaysian, russian, turkish, italian, dutch
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: tennis, lacrosse, skiing, baseball, golf, climbing, surfing
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, airplane, tram, jet-ski, skateboard, snowmobile
 1. the chinese is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is the person who's sport is golf##1
 3. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is the dutch##1
 6. the nigerian is the person driving the tram##1
 7. the nigerian is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 8. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
11. the turkish is on the right of the nigerian##1
12. the person driving the boat is the chinese##1
13. the russian is on the left of the nigerian##1
14. the russian is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
15. the chinese is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Nationality   | italian | dutch      | russian     | nigerian  | turkish | malaysian | chinese |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | tennis | climbing | skiing | surfing | baseball   | golf  |
| Transport     | airplane   | skateboard     | snowmobile        | tram  | jet-ski   | quad-bike       | boat      |

