 9. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the librarian##1
11. the person driving the subway is the nurse##1
12. the bartender is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the electrician##1
14. the person driving the car is the person drinking lemonade##1
