 4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
 5. the thai is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating peas is in the middle##1
 8. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 9. the australian is the person watching crime movies##1
10. the thai is the person eating kale##1
11. the person watching epic movies is the nigerian##1
12. the person eating lettuce is the chinese##1
13. the british is on the far right##1
14. the person watching comedy movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching family movies##2
15. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

