 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the freelancer##1
 5. the fan of disco is the pilot##1
 6. the social-worker is in the middle##1
 7. the electrician is the fan of gospel##1
 8. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the fan of disco is the owner of the rat##1
10. the bartender is the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the left of the freelancer##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
14. the fan of pop is on the left of the pilot##1
15. the bartender is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

